graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        Controller[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Main Controller]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Webhook]
        HTTPRouteMgr[HTTPRoute Manager<br/>Gateway API Routing]
        RefGrantMgr[ReferenceGrant Manager<br/>Cross-Namespace Access]
        NetPolMgr[NetworkPolicy Manager<br/>Traffic Isolation]
        RBACMgr[RBAC Manager<br/>SA/Role/RoleBinding]
        ProxyConfig[kube-rbac-proxy Config<br/>Auth Proxy Config]
        DSPAIntegration[DSPA Integration<br/>Pipeline Secrets & RBAC]

        Controller -->|creates| HTTPRouteMgr
        Controller -->|creates| RefGrantMgr
        Controller -->|creates| NetPolMgr
        Controller -->|creates| RBACMgr
        Controller -->|generates| ProxyConfig
        Controller -->|integrates| DSPAIntegration
        Webhook -->|injects sidecar| ProxyConfig
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| HTTPRoute[HTTPRoute<br/>gateway.networking.k8s.io/v1]
    Controller -->|creates| ReferenceGrant[ReferenceGrant<br/>Cross-Namespace Permission]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Traffic Isolation]
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount<br/>Notebook Identity]
    Controller -->|creates| Secret[Secret<br/>Pipeline Tokens & TLS]

    HTTPRoute -->|routes to| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]
    KubeRBACProxy -->|authenticates via| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>SubjectAccessReview]
    KubeRBACProxy -->|proxies to| NotebookService[Notebook Service<br/>8888/TCP HTTP]

    Webhook -->|validates requests from| K8sAPI

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Gateway[Data Science Gateway<br/>Gateway API]
        KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller<br/>Creates StatefulSets]
        ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>TLS Certificates]
        DSPOperator[Data Science Pipelines Operator<br/>DSPA CRs]
    end

    HTTPRoute -->|parent ref| Gateway
    NotebookCR -->|created by| KubeflowController
    Secret -->|provisioned by| ServiceCA
    DSPAIntegration -->|watches| DSPOperator

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Creates Notebook CRs]
        TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundle<br/>ConfigMap]
    end

    Dashboard -->|creates| NotebookCR
    Controller -->|mounts| TrustedCA

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style HTTPRoute fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeRBACProxy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Gateway fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSPOperator fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
